duces porous\nextensions to the Wagner and K\\\"{u}ssner functions for transient aerofoil\nmotions or gust encounters, respectively.}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2019 00:52:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Nov 2020 15:37:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-01"}
