ty of attacking scenarios and demonstrates 92% accuracy. On a two\nyears old Samsung S9, zkSENSE's attestation takes around 3 seconds (when visual\nCAPTCHAs need 9.8 seconds) and consumes a negligible amount of battery.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2019 14:04:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 11:14:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 12:56:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 10:54:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
